{
  "stem": "3022.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was truly a person who believed in the laws that governed the Jewish people during the holidays or Passover.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He wouldn't eat, he wouldn't eat the bread that was distributed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He would hoard potatoes and live on the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was one of the men that was put in our car.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You have to understand they put about 110 people into one cattle car.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And our transport set out, and after a few hours, we got to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we stayed at the sidings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And all we know that the [GERMAN] was negotiating with the officials at Auschwitz not to unload us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because we were defense workers, and our destination was to go to Germany, as we later found out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "While we were there, we could see the chimneys smoking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And how callous were we at that time that we were even remarking that they must be burning children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because the smoke is lighter from the chimneys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "While we were standing at the siding, they brought a transport from Holland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They came in Pullman cars, dressed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They thought they were going to some labor camp someplace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And with suitcases they were being unloaded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we could see the SS and the Jewish camp inmates taking them and separating them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Fortunately, after the four hours, the [GERMAN] won over, and we proceeded.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The reason that he fought so hard for us is because if he lost us, he would have gone to the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This way, he had those Jews to watch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we went on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And this is in August, 1944.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was terribly hot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We were kept in the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
